#include <iostream>
#include<map>
#include<string>
#include<string.h>
using namespace std;

int main()
{
	map<string,int>month;
	month["JAN"]=0;
	month["FEB"]=1;
	month["MAR"]=2;
	month["APR"]=3;
	month["MAY"]=4;
	month["JUN"]=5;
	month["JUL"]=6;
	month["AUG"]=7;
	month["SEP"]=8;
	month["OCT"]=9;
	month["NOV"]=10;
	month["DEC"]=11;
	int a[]={0,31,28,31,30,31,30,31,31,30,31,30};
	int T,i;
	for(i=1;i<12;i++)
	{
		a[i]=a[i-1]+a[i];
	}
	
   cin>>T;
   char str[15];
   for(int j=1;j<=T;j++)
   {
   	cin>>str;
   	int day=(str[0]-48)*10+(str[1]-48);
   	char m[4];
   	for(i=0;i<3;i++)
   	 m[i]=str[i+3];
   	m[i]='\0';
   	int mo=month[m];
   	int year=(str[7]-48)*1000+(str[8]-48)*100+(str[9]-48)*10+(str[10]-48);
   	int t_days=a[mo]+day;
   	if(year%100==0)
   	 {
   	 	if(year%400==0)
   	 	 {
   	 	 	if(mo>=2)
   	 	 	 t_days++;
   	 	 }
   	 }
   	else if(year%4==0)
   	 {
   	 	 	if(mo>=2)
   	 	 	 t_days++;
   	 }
   	if(t_days<=300)
   	  cout<<"Case "<<j<<": "<<t_days<<" "<<"Hundreds"<<"\n";
   	 else if(t_days<=360)
   	   cout<<"Case "<<j<<": "<<t_days-300<<" "<<"Tens"<<"\n";
   	 else
   	   cout<<"Case "<<j<<": "<<t_days-360<<" "<<"Ones"<<"\n";
   }
    return 0;
}
